  "name": "Enchanting Smile",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/light_07.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You gain a +2 enhancement bonus on&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/bluff\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bluff</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/diplomacy\" rel=\"nofollow\">Diplomacy</a>, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/skills/intimidate\" rel=\"nofollow\">Intimidate</a>&nbsp;skill checks. This bonus increases by +1 for every five wizard levels you possess, up to a maximum of +6 at 20th level. At 20th level, whenever you succeed at a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\" rel=\"nofollow\">saving throw</a>&nbsp;against a spell of the enchantment school, that spell is reflected back at its caster, as per&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/s/spell-turning\" rel=\"nofollow\">spell turning</a>.</p>"
    },
